HEADWORD: Nebalia
<hw>Ne*ba"li*a</hw> <pr>(n⟦esl⟧*b⟦amac⟧"l⟦icr⟧*⟦adot⟧)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., of uncertain origin.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A genus of small marine Crustacea, considered the type of a
distinct order (<ord>Nebaloidea</ord>, or
<ord>Phyllocarida</ord>.)</def>⟦br⟧
